          "email": "yong.fan@whamcloud.com",
          "date": "2011-03-07 15:49:17.000000000",
          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "ORNL-2 Enable OBD_CONNECT_ATTRFID supporting on lustre-2.x",
        "message": "ORNL-2 Enable OBD_CONNECT_ATTRFID supporting on lustre-2.x\n\nTo drop redundant MDS-side RPC for root object revalidation when\nstats each item for traversing directory based on absolute path.\n\nSigned-off-by: nasf <yong.fan@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5f7c7755b4142ac1f23c66517e5919c1398e15b8\n"
      },
